lyrics:
[Verse]
Hydration, essential for our health
Gotta hydrate, take care of yourself
Sip it up, drink it down, keep it flowing
Water's the remedy, always worth knowing

[Chorus]
Drink that water, stay refreshed
Quench your thirst, you know it's the best
H2O, the elixir of life
Stay hydrated, it's the way to thrive
